title: [Underground Temple, Sunken Tomb]
description: Uneven floors slant underfoot, swerving with the curve of the passage.  Pebbly rubble mixed with a mounds of dirt adds a challenging element, and walls slick with moisture don't offer a secure handhold.  Rough gouges mar the way, revealing attempts to create some means to steady travel along this egress.
paths: Obvious exits: north, east, south, west
